The Bridal Centre, in Brisbane, shut down unexpectedly earlier this month . 
 Around 140 brides were left out of pocket and without a dress . 
 They created a Facebook page called 'Where's My Dress' so the women could connect and try to find alternative ways to get their dream dress . 
 Ladies and bridal companies started to donate dresses to the women . 
 Adele McKenzie was one of the women who have been left without a dress . 
